examples.en: We mortgaged our house to start Paul's business.
She mortgaged her house in order to buy the restaurant.
His house, his business, indeed, his whole life was heavily mortgaged.
There was some reason to suppose that all the mortgaged houses would speedily let.
I've mortgaged all my free time this week to the hospice and won't be able to come to the party.
